*Description*.!Caution!: Do not modify *Description* Section!, you can modify below *Description* Section
*Description*.BOT_TOKEN: You must enter the TOKEN of the your Bot
*Description*.NOTICE_CHANNEL_ID: You can set the Notice Channel(FSA Status Updae Channel
*Description*.UPDATE_RATE_ONLINE_FLIGHT_STATUS: You can set 'FSAirlines Live Flight Status' update rate(It is in seconds), Must be greater than or equal to 1.(Default:10) : It must be a number only.
*Description*.UPDATE_RATE_TOTAL_STATUS: You can set 'FSAirlines Total Flight Status' update rate(It is in minute), Must be greater than or equal to 1.(Default:1) : It must be a number only.
*Description*.ERROR_CORLOR: You can set Embed Error Color. (Default:FF0000 = Red Color)
*Description*.greenColor: Embed color that appears when loading Status. (Default:GREEN)
*Description*.VA_ID: You must enter the ID of the VA whose Status is to be called.
*Description*.VA_NAME: You can set name of the VA
